    <item>
      <title>Exane 因供应过剩削减石油巨头股票评级，埃克森美孚股价罕见下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/exxon-gets-rare-sell-as-exane-cuts-oil-majors-on-oversupply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预计原油价格将进一步下跌，法国巴黎银行证券部分析师下调了三大石油公司的评级，埃克森美孚公司获得了一年多来首次卖出评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/exxon-gets-rare-sell-as-exane-cuts-oil-majors-on-oversupply</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:49:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚正在洽谈完成德国主要炼油厂的股份出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/exxon-mobil-in-talks-to-close-share-sale-in-key-german-refinery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，埃克森美孚公司正在与其他股东进行深入谈判，为出售德国第二大炼油厂的股份铺平道路，该交易因今年早些时候的法院裁决而暂停。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/exxon-mobil-in-talks-to-close-share-sale-in-key-german-refinery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:47:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普拉博沃计划重新任命多位现任部长加入内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/prabowo-plans-to-reappoint-many-current-ministers-to-his-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托表示，他的内阁可能由现任领导人佐科·维多多领导的“多名部长”组成，此举可确保东南亚最大经济体的政策连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/prabowo-plans-to-reappoint-many-current-ministers-to-his-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:43:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟测试银行家对欧洲大陆证券化债务的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/eu-sounds-out-finance-industry-on-securitization-debt-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟正在推进促进其资产支持证券市场的计划，并收集金融行业对一系列潜在措施的反馈，其中包括建立覆盖整个大陆的证券化平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/eu-sounds-out-finance-industry-on-securitization-debt-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 10:33:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长卡济米尔对下周降息仅持反对态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ecb-s-kazimir-not-convinced-on-october-cut-without-key-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员彼得·卡西米尔是迄今为止唯一真正反对下周进行年内第三次降息的人——尽管这一结果看起来越来越有把握。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ecb-s-kazimir-not-convinced-on-october-cut-without-key-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 09:02:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
